import React from 'react'
import PropTypes from "prop-types"
import { Button, Form, FormGroup, Label, Input, FormText, Container } from 'reactstrap'

const NewApartment = props => {
  return(
    <>
      <Container>
        <Form>
          <FormGroup>
            <Label htmlFor="address">Street Address</Label>
            <Input type="text" name="address" id="address" placeholder="" />
          </FormGroup>
          <FormGroup>
            <Label htmlFor="city">City</Label>
            <Input type="text" name="password" id="city" placeholder="" />
          </FormGroup>
          <FormGroup>
            <Label htmlFor="state">State</Label>
            <Input type="select" name="state" id="state">
              <option>CA</option>
              <option>2</option>
              <option>3</option>
              <option>4</option>
              <option>5</option>
            </Input>
          </FormGroup>
          <FormGroup>
            <Label htmlFor="zip">Zip</Label>
            <Input type="text" name="zip" id="zip" placeholder="" />
          </FormGroup>
          <FormGroup>
            <Label htmlFor="country">Country</Label>
            <Input type="text" name="country" id="country" placeholder="" />
          </FormGroup>
          <FormGroup>
            <Label htmlFor="building_manager">Building Manager</Label>
            <Input type="text" name="building_manager" id="building_manager" placeholder="" />
          </FormGroup>
          <FormGroup>
            <Label htmlFor="phone">Phone Number</Label>
            <Input type="text" name="phone" id="phone" placeholder="" />
          </FormGroup>
          <FormGroup>
            <Label htmlFor="hours">Contact Hours</Label>
            <Input type="text" name="hours" id="hours" placeholder="" />
          </FormGroup>
          <FormGroup>
            <Label htmlFor="image_url">Image URL</Label>
            <Input type="text" name="image_url" id="image_url" placeholder="" />
          </FormGroup>
          <FormGroup>
            <Label htmlFor="subject">Subject</Label>
            <Input type="text" name="subject" id="subject" placeholder="" />
          </FormGroup>
          <FormGroup>
            <Label htmlFor="description">Description</Label>
            <Input type="textarea" name="description" id="description" />
          </FormGroup>

          <Button>Submit</Button>
        </Form>
      </Container>
    </>
  )
}

export default NewApartment
